{"type":null,"faqId":32755,"title":"为什么浏览Pictures文件中的照片会出现缓冲拖影的现象？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">手机打开图片时，会先显示图片的缩略图，这个时候显示不清晰，然后手机会对图片进行区域解码，这个时候会更为清晰，所以对于一些图片细节较为丰富的照片就能够看到如贴砖式的刷新。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7457","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748401000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":5,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"照片,图片,图库,缓冲,拖影","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}